com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface Part

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PartAccent, PartAudioIn, PartDrum, PartKeyboard, PartStretchSlice
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PartAccentImpl, PartAudioInImpl, PartDrumImpl, PartImpl, PartKeyboardImpl, PartStretchSliceImpl

    public interface Part
    A representation of the model object 'Part'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Label
    • Level
    • Motion Sequence Status

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getPart()
